  "detailed_description": "Oldage is a turnbased strategy game with unique characters, charm, and originality. You can create hundreds of combinations of units, weaving a unique strategy each game. <br>Finally, a 0 RNG game that is easy to learn, but hard to master! For FREE! <br>It comes with a competitive ranked ladder, rewarding those with the best strategies! There is also an ELO system, try to become ranked in the top 100!<br><br>There are currently 5 Ranks:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658320/extras/d5e35f25ad205bee00f1d70e6cdc7393.webp?t=1546280782\" width=187 height=55 /></span> Student: 900+ Elo<br></li><li> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658320/extras/f109b6d5cc8bda6479ee38d8c3f3f7fd.webp?t=1546280782\" width=187 height=55 /></span> Scholar: 900 - 1100 Elo<br></li><li> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658320/extras/7f06b37f1e278ad52d2e3a8e5c1fdfe8.webp?t=1546280782\" width=187 height=55 /></span> Senior: 1100 - 1300 Elo<br></li><li> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658320/extras/3d302dc3c056d00528aa7914f11d2a79.webp?t=1546280782\" width=187 height=55 /></span> Sovereign: 1300 - 1500 Elo<br></li><li> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658320/extras/9485b33175b84df3b70c220a3a86e8e0.webp?t=1546280782\" width=187 height=55 /></span> Scarlet: 1500+ Elo</li></ul><br>And there are prizes for each rank! <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Scholar Priest: <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/658320/extras/18959254429a454